settings.custom_liquid: How Does The Consulting Work?

01

Meeting with our Shopify Experts

To understand your requirement, brand story and vibe of online store, our team of experts will discuss with you via meeting call or Google form to understand all your requirements.

Also, in this step, we'll follow up with you after the meeting call via any communication channel that is most convenient for you: Email, WhatsApp, Slack, Skype, etc.
02

Designing

We analyze your requirements in advance, then we plan the design and setup over time. After that, the general principles like headers, pages, and collections are designed and given to you to review.
03

Customizing

During our discussions about the design concept, we also asked the client to submit ideas for customizations. We'll advise you on a suitable Shopify app or customization according to your request.
04

Delivery & Testing

We provide you with a suitable design for you to check and comment. After you are satisfied, our developer will proceed to implement it on your Shopify site.
